*Velik* problem je da se ne zna rešenje. (The *big* problem is that we don't know the solution.)

*Velika* je šansa da ćemo uspeti. (There is a *big* chance that we will succeed.)

Došao je *veliki* broj ljudi. (A *large* number of people came.)

Nepopravljiva je *veličina* nastale štete. (The *magnitude* of the damage caused is irreparable.)

*Veličanstven* je pogled na dolinu. (The view of the valley is *magnificent*.)